source.name: 2007 Veterans' Insurance Expenditure by State and Congressional District
source.description: 2007 Veteran life insurance expenditures by state and county.  Expenditures were derived from Insurance Actuarial reports that used the total Insurance program cash disbursed.  The total cash disbursed was prorated by in-force data by state, which was further prorated by county and congressional district.
